title: For Sale:  FOR SALE ADDS WITH NO CITY = SCAM
location: North Carolina, North Carolina, United States
postcontent: All "North Carolina, North Carolina" For sale adds with no city listed that I have responded to are SCAMS. I have responded to over 25 of them. NONE were legitimate. They are always people wanting you to wire money, send, cash etc and when I  traced the originating ip from the emails, in all but 3 out of 25 cases they are in foreign countries France, Nigeria, etc. None of the 3 that were in the US were where the seller said he or she was. They were all at least 1000 miles away. They are using mail forwarding to forward your payment across the country to make it harder to track them down by the time you find out they are not going to ship you anything and are just stealing your money. FLAG THESE ADDS AS SCAMS AND MOVE ON.

From Wikipedia: 
The Zastava M72 chambers and fires the 7.62x39mm M43 round. It is a gas-operated, air-cooled, drum-fed firearm with a fixed stock.
This weapon is a near copy of the Soviet RPK light machine gun. There are a few differences on the M72/M72A. It does not have a scope side rail mount, the butt is also different, having the shape of a regular AK-47 rifle. It has a reinforced receiver, night sights and no carrying handle. The barrel also differs from other RPK rifles because of the cooling fins to help with heat dissipation from prolonged fire. The M72 only appears with a heavy profile barrel as opposed to Russian and Romanian RPK rifles that can come in both light or heavy barrel configurations.

This specific M-72 was purchased locally about 3 years ago, roughly 400 rounds put through it, and cleaned after every use.  No failures ever experienced with a variety of ammo manufactures put through it.
